The evidence with the title 'Facebook survey scam - free argos gift card ' says Aug 9, 2012  ... Scams . Survey scams · like-farming scams · phishing scams  ... Message appearing on Facebook claims that users can receive a free £ 500 argos gift card just by clicking a link in the post .  ... The message is not an official Argos promotion .  ... Some versions ask users to join a bogus Facebook event page . 
